On social aspects, we need to continue building sustainable and cohesive communities through increased, viable and genuine peacebuilding initiatives to address underlying causes of animosity. Communities must be made to understand that others matter.
We should scale up and leverage our position as a technology-savvy country to address access to services, quick response to pandemics, droughts, disasters and restoration of services where they are disrupted.



